<h1><span id="Polish_Defence_Deferred">Polish Defence Deferred</span></h1>
<h3><span id="2...b5">2...b5</span></h3>
<p>With this move, Black prevents White from playing c4 and prepares his queen's bishop to be fianchettoed.
</p>
<p><b>1.d4 Nf6 2. Nf3 b5</b>
</p>
